body_html:
Yes, thanks, boche! It turned out release 1.1 was cut just 3 days before the fix.

The fix will be part of the next release, which will be in the next two months or so and rc0 in about one month.

In the meantime, you may consider using the nightly build here: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow
